          "reviewBody": "My daughter is studying since beginning. I find that the school is one of the best ones in this area. The student's progress is quite good and well qualified faculty. UI bookelts, session plans everything you need for your child's development is there.They can improve infrastructure a bit the furniture is not so comfortable but else in all other parameters this is the best school.",
