          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Hi Everyone! I would like to share my awesome experience with DPSGPV with everyone. We had moved to Gurugram last year and I didn't think much before admitting my kid sro DPSG as I thought the school had a great legacy of more than 42 years. I always wanted my kids to get admission in an IB curriculum school and DPSG'S IB syllabus is very interactive and research oriented for kids. The school pays a lot of attention to both scholastic and co- scholastic activities. The faculty is very well experienced and they know how to take out the best in a child! Also the school ambience is very nice and air-conditioned so it's comfortable for kids. They also have a world class swimming facility with good trainers. Its got all that I wanted for in a school for children and am highly satisfied also with the school and my kids performance! Overall excellent faculty, facilities ambience for kids...",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
